WEBVTT


00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.480
So last week, after I filmed myself cleaning my room,

00:00:03.481 --> 00:00:06.161
I had a lot of questions and comments about my bed,

00:00:06.162 --> 00:00:07.321
which is super high,

00:00:07.322 --> 00:00:10.161
which my husband custom built so that we would have storage underneath,

00:00:10.162 --> 00:00:12.181
because we only have about three feet

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:13.520
on either side of the bed in this room,

00:00:13.521 --> 00:00:15.241
so we really don't have a lot of room for storage,

00:00:15.242 --> 00:00:18.001
and we needed that. So we custom built this bed,

00:00:18.002 --> 00:00:22.061
and as you can see, it's almost waist height on me.

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:22.840
And I'm pregnant,

00:00:22.841 --> 00:00:25.441
so this is becoming increasingly harder to get into bed.

00:00:25.442 --> 00:00:27.681
But I will show you how I get into bed for now,

00:00:27.682 --> 00:00:30.021
and then my husband is going to build me a stool

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:34.140
for when I'm more heavily pregnant. I just put my knee up

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:36.965
and hoist myself in.
